title: WHIRLING F1 ORB / vicquemare esprit afterthought
description: What a hell... *are* we from the same station?

dialogueTree.title: Esprit de Corps: "Okay, the man with the sunglasses a..."
dialogueTree.english: Okay, the man with the sunglasses and his *hypothetical Station 41*. Weird, right?
dialogueTree.polish: No dobra, facet w okularach i jego *hipotetyczny 41. komisariat*. Dziwne, co?
dialogueTree.belarusian: Ну добра, хлопец у акулярах і яго *гіпатэтычны 41-ы камісарыят*. Дзіўна, так?

links.title: Esprit de Corps: "There's something we're missing her..."
links.english: There's something we're missing here... something you can't put our finger on. You know what -- just ask him. I know it sounds crazy (and you'll probably get laughed at). But still...
links.polish: Coś tu jest nie tak, choć nie umiesz stwierdzić jasno, o co chodzi. Wiesz co? Po prostu go spytaj. Wiem, że to brzmi wariacko (i pewnie cię wyśmieje), ale mimo wszystko...
links.belarusian: Нешта тут не так, хоць ты не можаш дакладна вызначыць, у чым справа. Ведаеш што? Проста спытай у яго. Ведаю, што гэта гучыць вар'яцка (і, напэўна, ён цябе пасмяе), але ўсё роўна...

links.title: You: "I was thinking the same thing. I sh..."
links.english: I was thinking the same thing. I should just ask him if we're from the same station.
links.polish: Myślałem właśnie to samo. Powinienem go po prostu zapytać, czy jesteśmy z tego samego komisariatu.
links.belarusian: Я якраз думаў пра тое самае. Мне варта проста спытаць яго, ці мы з таго самага аддзялення міліцыі.

links.title: Esprit de Corps: "Yes. Just cross it off the list. It..."
links.english: Yes. Just cross it off the list. It's probably not true though.
links.polish: Tak. Po prostu skreśl to już z listy. Choć to pewnie nieprawda.
links.belarusian: Так. Проста выдалі гэта ўжо са спісу. Хаця гэта, напэўна, няпраўда.

links.title: You: "It's impossible. I don't want to wa..."
links.english: It's impossible. I don't want to waste my time.
links.polish: To niemożliwe. Nie chcę marnować czasu.
links.belarusian: Гэта немагчыма. Я не хачу марнаваць час.

links.title: Esprit de Corps: "Of course. Yes. It's preposterous."
You: "I guess it was kind of weird, yes."
links.english: I guess it was kind of weird, yes.
links.polish: Tak, w sumie było to trochę dziwne.
links.belarusian: Так, увогуле гэта было крыху дзіўна.

links.title: You: "No, this whole interaction was perf..."
links.english: No, this whole interaction was perfectly normal.
links.polish: Nie, to była najzupełniej normalna interakcja.
links.belarusian: Не, гэта была зусім звычайная ўзаемадзеянне.

links.title: You: "Frankly I'm way past caring or wond..."
links.english: Frankly I'm way past caring or wondering. [Discard thought.]
links.polish: Szczerze, to ani mnie to już nie obchodzi, ani nie zastanawia. [Odrzuć myśl].
links.belarusian: Шчыра кажучы, мяне гэта ўжо ні не цікавіць, ні не здзіўляе. [Адкінь думку].
